					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There's a lot less standardization when it comes to assemblers. MASM has directives that do both things: <a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/4bd8b239.aspx" class="postlink">IF</a> vs <a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/f4x287ff.aspx" class="postlink">.IF</a>.</div>

