					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I don't think there is much of a limit on how far you could go with enough macro code. As it is, none of these generate a lot of code - the signed comparison generates the most. If more complicated expressions were wanted they would have to result in more complex code being output. Interesting that MASM has support for this kind of thing.<br /><br />EDIT: <s>Actually there is a pretty bad error in the code highlevel.h due to a search and replace doing more than I expected, I&#39;ll update this post when it is fixed..</s> Fixed, links still valid.</div>

